<h2 id="future-plans">Future plans</h2>

<p>A remaining challenge is the data-plane federation of both testbeds, to enable experiments spanning both testbeds in a
controlled networking environment. We will explore how to achieve that by interconnecting both testbeds to Internet Software Defined eXchange
points (SDX), which would allow us to provide on-demand Level-2 link stitching, to provide per-experiment overlays.</p>

